sellerAgent.name: The Good Life Group Top Team on Lanier

data.description: Welcome home to 5969 Warpath Road. This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is conveniently located close to schools, shopping, dining and more. Lake Lanier  is just a few minutes away so bring your boat or RV with plenty of parking for both. You will immediately feel right at home upon entering the 2-story foyer. Spacious dining room is the perfect gathering place for family dinners. Large family room with vaulted ceilings & wood burning fireplace. Bright sunroom overlooking the private backyard for all of your plants and a place to enjoy your morning coffee. Airy kitchen with new granite countertops and stylish backsplash. All stainless steel appliances included. Huge mudroom/laundry room located right off the kitchen. Private bonus room perfect for guest bedroom, rec room or workshop. Master on main with his & hers closets. Relax in the ensuite after a long day in the jetted tub or amazing shower with rainfall shower head and dual vanities. Two additional spacious bedrooms located upstairs with huge walk-in closets. Full bath with double vanity. The partially fenced private .49 acre lot is ideal place to enjoy company at the fire pit or relax on the porch. Storage shed for all of your tools. Peaceful neighborhood with no HOA. You will not want to miss out on this one!
